&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits and Growth:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Best-in-breed onboarding and leadership enablement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generous global benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intra-departmental mentor and buddy programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;New hire stock equity (RSUs) and employee stock purchase plan (ESPP)&lt;/li&gt;
